{"tid":1878266,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請勿口爆]鐘南山：患者的尿液、糞便、血液、唾液、鼻涕、胃液和精液都有病毒","createTime":"2020-02-13T13:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T13:32:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9b5a023316d0f2762d51af14de3b6aff69a669","tid":1878266,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:22:56.000Z","msg":"鍾南山團隊在患者多種分泌物和排泄物發現病毒<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】國家衛健委高級別專家組組長鍾南山的團隊，在患者的多種分泌物和排泄物發現新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山團隊成員之一、廣州大學附屬第一醫院教授鄭則廣指，團隊在患者的尿液、糞便、血液、唾液、鼻涕、胃液和精液都分離出活病毒，但在淚液和汗液就未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員亦在患者的手掌皮膚、指甲及頭髮發現病毒核酸，認為可以肯定病毒可以透過接觸或透過患者的尿液和糞便傳播。團隊已經嘗試多種藥物和方法治療患者，初步取得良好效果。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國家科學院院士陳凱先出席上海市政府記者會時透露，研究發現一種抗瘧疾藥物能抑制新型冠狀病毒的活性，國家科技部和衞健委已經列為臨床試驗藥物，並啟動有關試驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=380489\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380489&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvVuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=9384ec1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380489&h=44ee210c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=380489</a>"},{"pid":"6baf3a238d68b296334e25dabda8d3d4c6470afe","tid":1878266,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e01aa21e691c3cb9d2586650b147b026ba416d6","tid":1878266,"uid":298104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"係咪叫個患者打完飛機俾佢地取樣本？？？"},{"pid":"0dd4465d691d6a5a5d447aab837bca685aa120e7","tid":1878266,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e01aa21e691c3cb9d2586650b147b026ba416d6","tid":1878266,"uid":298104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"係咪叫個患者打完飛機俾佢地取樣本？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"用針拮春袋抽，好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a7e839f760e760b9f68225a286f6686f85ca92","tid":1878266,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dd4465d691d6a5a5d447aab837bca685aa120e7","tid":1878266,"uid":12404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e01aa21e691c3cb9d2586650b147b026ba416d6","tid":1878266,"uid":298104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"係咪叫個患者打完飛機俾佢地取樣本？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:31:26.000Z","msg":"用針拮春袋抽，好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}